node.text:
Those gym withdrawals 🥺❤️ TAG your girl who is over lockdown workouts 🙋🏼‍♀️_ wearing my new @tahirabykb #madeinLA collection! 
-
-
Missing the Mecca. I filmed a real and raw full lower body session. Started with kick back for isolation work to get those glutes nice and warm. Followed with some strength work on my squats - I ended up doing 7 sets of 5-6 reps, lots of walking lunges and finished on single leg leg press! It’s not about how many exercises you cram into a session, it’s your intensity and focus on the exercise in front of you!
